{"tid":251482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞賊尖沙咀警署外落手　搶走男子60元","createTime":"2017-05-21T03:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T04:16:23.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8db15b18a7bb91ad0c00dcd4966990cdd7e7bb7","tid":251482,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:31:36.000Z","msg":"沙膽南亞賊尖沙咀警署外搶劫！凌晨3時許，一名姓鍾（30歲）男子途經彌敦道尖沙咀警署外，突然有一名南亞裔男子走近，指事主搶走其物品。事主與其理論時，被對方搶去一個袋，內有60港元現金及一張八達通卡。 <br />\n<br />\n糾纏間事主遭賊人揮拳打傷手部，賊人得手後逃去，事主報警求助，其後送院治理。涉案的南亞漢身高1.65米，警員在附近兜截無果，案件列作行劫，由油尖警區刑事調查隊跟進。"},{"pid":"e88187b6ce77c847020ff60ca1f5e829154545fb","tid":251482,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65dda75b69f797da3faeffe41cce1137ec06ead7","tid":251482,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:33:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"647c555fcc6c569ce5b37fb0ac34c4dce2091163","tid":251482,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:34:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbab749b9f694e469f0f3a918d7e67a5e9617108","tid":251482,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾十蚊走去報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾十蚊都係犯法"},{"pid":"6f94f41445b28f48f901fc4efe793068ff3af5f5","tid":251482,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:35:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾十蚊走去報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係 人地南亞人生活好辛苦"},{"pid":"6b4721677f7febed351040c32ca8cde11ba